org.oasis.openc2.lycan

Class OpenC2Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.oasis.openc2.lycan.OpenC2Message

  • public class OpenC2Message
extends java.lang.Object
    OpenC2Message is the base object that should be used when working with OpenC2 messaging. At a minimum, all OpenC2 messages must have an action and a target. Actuator and modifiers are optional.
